{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Flames in Modern Europe is not just a real-time global strategy game; it's also an opportunity to immerse yourself in the interesting and captivating events of modern Europe, such as Euromaidan and the Revolution of Dignity! Build a powerful economy of the Old Continent, or start a war against a neighboring state! Develop your nation, overcome political crises, and become part of the most exciting moments in modern history!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342400/extras/Screenshot_2024-11-23_175211.png?t=1737978343\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MAIN MECHANICS</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Courses: In the country menu, you have several courses, such as political and economic. This is your plan to achieve greatness in Europe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decisions: Make important decisions for your country, such as government propaganda or money printing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Economy: Build new structures that will work for the benefit of the state. Use the budget menu to adjust the expenses and efficiency of various areas of the country, such as construction, research, the army, and administration. Don't forget about the average salary!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342400/extras/image\u0443\u0443.png?t=1737978343\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Research: Investigate new technologies that will help your country become the most progressive.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342400/extras/\u0441\u0441\u0432.png?t=1737978343\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Army: No further explanation needed... Press the red button!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a fictional alternate history. All events, characters, 